{"tid":2162782,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"破局方案，大家點睇","createTime":"2020-08-18T09:50:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T14:06:10.000Z","uid":240642,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2b7a109fe167e713c726deadb6e79c5fb5b23a07","tid":2162782,"uid":240642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:50:08.000Z","msg":"既然泛民話為左「顧全大局」留低嘅，咁就做下面嘅嘢啦！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>1) 公投決定薪酬點用</ins></strong><br />\n你話係守住議會，但係冇民意授權，咁用呢個方法畀大家決定你份糧點洗囉。一係你請初選入圍嘅做議員助理，一係你捐左佢，再唔係大家覺得你可以自己袋嘅，你咪攞你應得嘅比例囉。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>2) 只投關鍵反對票，其他一概唔投</ins></strong><br />\n始終你地係冇被市民授權，你地既然話係要守尾門，唔該其他唔關事嘅議案唔好投喇。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>3) 如果總辭嘅意見仲係主流，你都係應該走</ins></strong><br />\n如果做左以上兩項民調有六成、甚至2/3以上係支持照辭職嘅，你地都應該尊重民意。<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？"},{"pid":"2e6c8c567a93314e80721df68a081175e730261e","tid":2162782,"uid":240642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:51:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d1850944fc0b50031eb6f73f83e07d321240134","tid":2162782,"uid":240642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e132d43d6d125fc7b0575c4f8801bcfe56b2674","tid":2162782,"uid":240642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:04:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afdf8cc66b018bf658cc692e1913adb334d35c33","tid":2162782,"uid":240642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:32:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2aacfbd7cc637291b135bc38629b9dde4a4b987","tid":2162782,"uid":240642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:34:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e932db44b579acf9f44380e05e1e9a438d9083eb","tid":2162782,"uid":240642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:39:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e64864f6c34662432ccb7dd05d7083eebd6f7121","tid":2162782,"uid":240642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:44:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a87099dd7ba937b378bb948ebf24fb2acdad9154","tid":2162782,"uid":364663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T10:53:55.000Z","msg":"扣左供樓d錢先霸公投得唔得？"},{"pid":"38ce5518422872db99579a74f5b6c64feb890114","tid":2162782,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:24:52.000Z","msg":"(3), 有明顯民意支持唔留, 就唔會搞到而家咁啦<br />\n而家就係留同唔留都係大約一半半<br />\n<br />\n解決方案: 以二級議會, 解決去留爭議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2162332/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2162332/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"f00aec6a390baed261850aff71a90ffaee6c013f","tid":2162782,"uid":240642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:06:10.000Z","msg":"推"}]}